{"tid":2256823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（川普贏戰役、拜登贏戰爭 ）民調專家：川普難再創逆轉勝奇蹟","createTime":"2020-10-24T16:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T17:30:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d8bb6dd3c79f597ccb25a9dae57ebb33841eed","tid":2256823,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"美國總統川普與民主黨總統候選人拜登，結束最後一場辯論會後，均立即投入各州造勢衝刺，在拜登民調持續保持領先的情況下，川普陣營寄望再創4年前打破各大民調預測，奇蹟般勝選。不過，共和黨民調專家和策士倫茨（Frank Luntz）認為，川普沒有足夠時間追上拜登，即使民調再次失準，也「幾乎不可能」逆轉勝。<br />\n<br />\n倫茨23日接受美國媒體CNBC訪問，針對當天的川普、拜登辯論會，指出川普在辯論會上勝過拜登，「但是這將不足以讓他贏得連任」。他說，這場「小勝利」，讓川普爭取到一些尚未決定投給誰的選民，並且縮小比賽差距，「但是最終，我想是拜登贏得這場戰爭」。剩下這11天不夠讓川普趕上拜登在全國和搖擺州的領先幅度。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，4年前民調失準，但是當時民主黨候選人希拉蕊僅領先幾個百分點，這次拜登的民調領先幅度，超過任何統計誤差，而且，這次民調專家都謹慎得多。<br />\n<br />\n他還指出，辯論會最後一個提問「若當選總統，在就職演說要對沒有投給你的人說什麼」，川普以批評拜登為何不適合擔任總統作為回答，有力但是調性負面，拜登則說「我是代表全民的總統」，充滿正面、積極性，是拜登得以贏得選民民心的理由。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3331514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3331514&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=b0e4bcb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3331514&h=1ae54174\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3331514</a>"},{"pid":"2e6c15200ec5606f0fbe41a1d397aea1b575b18d","tid":2256823,"uid":209890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:08:46.000Z","msg":"大數據先係最準確"},{"pid":"f7f170018394e52a454ece350e48842dbbc71fa9","tid":2256823,"uid":186882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:09:39.000Z","msg":"共和黨都有食屎專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24443c113777bf5227e68d10c2efeb5e574e9d65","tid":2256823,"uid":286897,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:14:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4869eb6a13fcf27c703506611b4ae47c1079b44","tid":2256823,"uid":144626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:15:35.000Z","msg":"FC下好d, 華文新聞好易斷章取義<br />\n<br />\n呢篇點睇，如果再唔準佢都冇得撈，梗係想佢準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.foxnews.com/politics/pollster-frank-luntz-if-trump-defies-polls-again-in-2020-my-profession-is-done.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fpollster-frank-luntz-if-trump-defies-polls-again-in-2020-my-profession-is-done.amp&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=af8906e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/www.foxnews.com/politics/pollster-frank-luntz-if-trump-defies-polls-again-in-2020-my-profession-is-done.amp</a><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I hate to acknowledge it, because that's my industry &mdash; at least partially &mdash; but the public will have no faith. No confidence. Right now, the biggest issue is the trust deficit,&rdquo; Luntz said in response to Baier asking how pollsters will fare if they are wrong in predicting the 2020 presidential election. &ldquo;Pollsters did not do a good job in 2016. So, if Donald Trump surprises people, if Joe Biden had a 5- or 6-point lead, my profession is done"},{"pid":"2ab32151a98d49d4a635311a1f126ef503fb323b","tid":2256823,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:15:46.000Z","msg":"China Joe已經夠票<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d2c38ad3e981c732ca4cffc5cdac617fbd6bd1","tid":2256823,"uid":70013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:27:17.000Z","msg":"同你較早前開嗰個post好似嚟自同一篇嘢<br />\n都係嗰個民調專家"},{"pid":"7b05b7f36d64c68f48a6b2edfc9d013